    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine currently has a blown head gasket and the transmission is slipping badly. The exterior shows heavy rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several large dents and faded clear coat. The interior has seen better days, with significant tearing in the driver's seat and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal candidate for a complete restoration project or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
