      "description": "Ready for a rewarding project? This vehicle is in poor condition and is looking for a dedicated owner who can give it the mechanical and cosmetic TLC it needs! It's a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a restoration challenge with a lot of potential upside.",
